<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <title>Alpha blog CMS</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family:
          Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
          sans-serif;
      }

      .cms-switch {
        position: fixed;
        right: 18px;
        bottom: 18px;
        z-index: 1000;
        width: min(380px, calc(100vw - 36px));
        border: 1px solid rgba(45, 56, 48, 0.14);
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 252, 0.94);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(20, 26, 22, 0.14);
        color: #1d241f;
        backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(1.05);
      }

      .cms-switch summary {
        cursor: pointer;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        font-weight: 760;
      }

      .cms-switch div {
        padding: 0 14px 14px;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .cms-switch a {
        display: inline-flex;
        margin-top: 8px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        background: #2f6d58;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 760;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body data-pagefind-ignore>
    <details class="cms-switch" open>
      <summary>推荐使用新版块编辑器</summary>
      <div>
        <p>Sveltia 仍保留为兜底入口，但复杂正文建议使用自研块编辑器。新版支持可编辑表格、结构化内容块，并保存为 MDX 短代码。</p>
        <a href="/admin/editor/">进入 Alpha editor</a>
      </div>
    </details>
    <script is:inline>
      window.CMS_MANUAL_INIT = true;
    </script>
    <script is:inline src="https://unpkg.com/@sveltia/cms@0.167.3/dist/sveltia-cms.js"></script>
    <script is:inline src="/admin/cms.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
